Q33.Write a PHP script to create student.xml file which contains student roll no,
name, address, college and course. Print students detail of specific course in
tabular format after accepting course as input.
Answer::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
1st Page 
<?php
if(isset($_POST['t1']))
{
    $course = $_POST['t1'];

    $xml = simplexml_load_file("stud.xml");

    echo "<table border=1>";
    echo "<tr>";
    echo "<th>Roll no</th>";
    echo "<th>Name</th>";
    echo "<th>Address</th>";
    echo "<th>College</th>";
    echo "<th>Course</th>";
    echo "</tr>";

    foreach($xml->stud as $s)
    {
        if($s->course == $course)
        {
            echo "<tr>";
            echo "<td>".$s->rno."</td>";
            echo "<td>".$s->name."</td>";
            echo "<td>".$s->address."</td>";
            echo "<td>".$s->college."</td>";
            echo "<td>".$s->course."</td>";
            echo "</tr>";
        }
    }
    echo "</table>";
}
?>
